column5: Here are a few of some of the fish I caught in 2008. Hope you like.             Thanks again for looking  :clapping:
Wow, all pigs! Nice work, thanks for givin' us all that teaser for next year!
Great year in review and pics Lungelarry  Those ski's are gigantic and them smallies football size    Congratulations and thanks for sharing Leechman
Awesome!!! Can I go musky fishing with you next year?
Were you catching the Bass to use for bait for the Mucksies???  Great pics!!!
nice pics. we love the fish porn. nice to see your year was very good.
Good stuff LungeLarry. It's nice to see that you're doing as well as ever. Thanks for taking the time to post....great pics!
Very nice Pics ......   Congrats on a , What i would say good year...
some really nice fish, thanks for sharing!
Now thats a good year!

Awesome fish .... but, how about a smile next time you haul in one of those monsters though ?!  Alot of stone-faced pics there !  Smile!  You're out there, catching fish.  Be happy about !!!!!!  Never mind.  I'm just jealous because I didn't get out as much as I wanted to last year
Some GREAT fish there Larry! Thanks for the porn..
Those are some awsome fish. What lake or lakes were they caught on?
All very solid fish! Looks like you had a pretty good summer. Cheers,
Nice pics! Apparently you attended Lew's tutorial on: a) how to catch skis how to smile for the camera! Thanks for posting! HH
Arent you the famous lunkerlarry???  word is you get the biggest fish year round!  great job on holding your reputation!  verry nice skies.
WooHoo   got to love bass fishing!!! Very nice pictures and looks like you have had no problem catching some BIG fish last year,  Thanks for sharing!
Thanks guys , I,m glad you enjoyed.
Awesome mixed bag of bruisers man !!!.  .well done...cheers
Fine fish Larry.  Enjoyed the pics.  Good luck in 09.
Like they said above!  Would love some posts as they came.  Great job
Great fish!  Even a nice norther in the mix.  Those are some great musky.  THose smallies are all footballs. Nice!
Nice fish!
